1 RESOLVED BY THE ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, That
2 for the 36th Special Session of the Nevada Legislature, no
3 allowances will be paid for members of the Assembly for
4 periodicals, stamps, stationery or the use of telephones and no
5 allowances will be paid for the Speaker, Speaker Pro Tempore,
6 Majority Leader, Minority Leader or chair of a committee of the
7 Assembly for postage, telephone tolls or other charges for
8 communications; and be it further
9 RESOLVED, That this resolution becomes effective upon
